    "answer_id" : 12960618,
    "question_id" : 12960554,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Lots of tools expect <code>is</code> or <code>get</code> and won't likely recognize <code>are</code>.</p>\n\n<p>Try rephrasing them, like <code>getDogsAreFuzzy()</code> or <code>getStoresAreOpen()</code> or things like that for better compatibility and conventions.</p>\n"
